bureau_data.description: Required if request to call Equifax or TransUnion

inquiry_data.description: Information required by the respective bureau.

client_app_id.description: Pre-defined two-digit code. Required for all requests.

subcode.description: Optional. If not provided, extract from inquiry string if provided.

solution_id.description: Required if not provided in inquiry string via GO- keyword.

inquiry.description: Required to pull ARF from DCR. 'models' object and 'inquiry_data' are mutually exclusive
inquiry.example: TCA1 MS2X 1234567ABC AUSTIN, SAN 000000000;CA-871 WINNIG STREET/VICTORY ST 12121;Y-1958;T-3F;UNLKPQ;GETPIN;V-07;

include_credit_profile_in_response.description: true/false; if true, return full ARF content in response. Default is true.

include_model_result_in_response.description: true/false; if true, return model score/attribute results (in addition to segment 130 in ARF). Default is false.

include_model_input_in_response.description: true/false; applicable only for custom models in GO; true - returns all inputs sent to the model

reuse_credit_report.description: true/false; true: for second call to go-inquiry for a previously process client_transaction_id, to support models with custom attributes

model_specific_custom_data.description: required if requested models contain custom data attributes.
